Ease off on the brakes!

711
01:00:45,742 --> 01:00:47,869
Brakes, now.

712
01:00:53,116 --> 01:00:55,880
Stop, damn you. Stop.

713
01:01:43,800 --> 01:01:47,065
What the hell happened here?

714
01:01:47,170 --> 01:01:49,070
<i>I don't know.</i>

715
01:01:50,673 --> 01:01:53,141
He must have got 'em both.

716
01:01:56,045 --> 01:01:59,242
Don't go back through
that train without this.

717
01:01:59,348 --> 01:02:03,944
Watch your step there.
Stay together. Don't go too far.

718
01:02:04,053 --> 01:02:06,613
Come on. Keep on moving,
everybody. Come on.

719
01:02:06,723 --> 01:02:12,127
Get yourselves a couple of fire axes
and search every damn inch of these cars.

720
01:02:12,228 --> 01:02:16,062
He could be anywhere.
And he's lethal, so stick together.

721
01:02:16,165 --> 01:02:18,395
And don't try to be heroes.

722
01:02:18,501 --> 01:02:21,299
If you just think you hear somethin',
you come hollerin' for help.

723
01:02:21,404 --> 01:02:23,304
Okay, chief.

724
01:02:23,406 --> 01:02:28,207
Keep moving.
Watch your step, please.

725
