736
01:03:30,273 --> 01:03:33,174
<i>Hey, you there, let go ofhim.</i>

737
01:03:34,477 --> 01:03:36,775
<i>- Herbie Green?
- Okay?</i>

738
01:03:36,879 --> 01:03:39,177
<i>Dan Irwin?</i>

739
01:03:39,282 --> 01:03:44,276
<i>I want the rest
of those masks off now. Hurry along there.</i>

740
01:03:44,387 --> 01:03:47,845
- How come it's just all my best friends
in the fucking world?
- What do we all have in common?

741
01:03:47,957 --> 01:03:50,892
- Jackson.
- You and me and Mitchy and the guys?

742
01:03:50,993 --> 01:03:54,520
Doc, we hurt him.

743
01:03:54,630 --> 01:03:58,760
- What are you talking about?
- Kenny Hampson. Your stunt with the corpse.

744
01:03:58,868 --> 01:04:01,234
Nobody'd do that
for a goddamn prank.

745
01:04:01,337 --> 01:04:04,738
It wasn't just a prank.
Doc, he was sick.

746
01:04:06,309 --> 01:04:10,006
I went to the hospital
just afterwards.

747
01:04:10,112 --> 01:04:12,103
They wouldn't let me see him.

748
01:04:12,215 --> 01:04:14,149
They said he'd killed
somebody before.

749
01:04:14,250 --> 01:04:17,151
