779
01:06:20,042 --> 01:06:23,671
We'll sit tight and when the train stops,
we'll play a trick on old Kenny.

780
01:06:23,779 --> 01:06:27,875
- The train is stopped.
- Then they better start it up again
'cause it's gonna...

781
01:06:27,984 --> 01:06:31,977
- He's back there with all of our friends!
- Let's hope so, huh?

782
01:06:32,088 --> 01:06:34,886
I don't believe you.

783
