We've gotta tell them!

784
01:06:38,494 --> 01:06:40,394
I'm not movin'.

785
01:06:43,566 --> 01:06:45,466
Every man for himself.

786
01:06:50,006 --> 01:06:52,531
Alana, don't.

787
01:06:52,641 --> 01:06:55,132
