805
01:10:40,803 --> 01:10:42,862
- I know who it is.
- What?

806
01:10:42,972 --> 01:10:45,634
- Where's the conductor?
- Back there. Come on.

807
01:10:50,779 --> 01:10:54,078
God, it was cold out there.
My feet are numb.

808
01:10:54,183 --> 01:10:56,151
I told you to stay in the car.

809
01:10:56,252 --> 01:10:59,847
Well, they made me get off.
I mean, they had to search here.

810
01:11:04,526 --> 01:11:07,324
Oh, I'm sorry.
Is something missing?

811
01:11:09,999 --> 01:11:11,990
<i>Geez, I was scared out there.</i>

812
01:11:12,101 --> 01:11:17,368
I couldn't find you, and I'm thinking
this wacko's gonna jump out at me any minute.

813
01:11:17,473 --> 01:11:19,941
Hey, I should have
used one of these.

814
01:11:22,111 --> 01:11:24,079
Yeah, this would have done.
What do you think?

815
01:11:26,348 --> 01:11:30,307
- Let's go back, Alana. They'll be coming back.
- Doc?

816
01:11:30,419 --> 01:11:33,354
- It's okay. I'm with the prez.
- Damn it.

817
01:11:38,127 --> 01:11:41,187
Yeah. Yeah, I know.

818
01:11:41,297 --> 01:11:44,630
Well, whatever.
Have you ever shoveled any coal?

819
01:11:44,733 --> 01:11:46,633
- No.
- He's on the train.

820
01:11:46,735 --> 01:11:50,193
- Why isn't she lying down somewhere?
- The magician!

821
01:11:50,306 --> 01:11:53,742
- Magician?
- I'll show you. Come on.

822
01:11:53,842 --> 01:11:55,969
