823
01:12:00,983 --> 01:12:04,646
<i>Doc, open up.</i>

824
01:12:04,753 --> 01:12:08,189
<i>Open up in there, please.</i>

825
01:12:08,290 --> 01:12:10,258
<i>Doc?</i>

826
01:12:11,293 --> 01:12:14,319
<i>Doc? I just left him in there.</i>

827
01:12:35,884 --> 01:12:38,409
Keep her outside.

828
01:13:06,081 --> 01:13:08,208
Don't go in there, miss.

829
01:14:15,083 --> 01:14:17,142
<i>Doc.!</i>

830
01:14:35,771 --> 01:14:38,467
You move out real quiet, darlin'.

831
01:14:38,574 --> 01:14:42,010
Hey, what's going on?

832
01:14:42,110 --> 01:14:45,602
We got the coffee maker workin', miss.

833
01:14:45,714 --> 01:14:48,239
Come on.

834
01:14:52,754 --> 01:14:56,554
<i>- Where is he?
- He's right back there.</i>

835
01:14:56,658 --> 01:14:59,024
Come on.

836
01:14:59,127 --> 01:15:01,027
Ken?

837
01:15:01,129 --> 01:15:05,031
<i>They made coffee out here.
I'll bring you in a cup, okay?</i>

838
01:15:14,443 --> 01:15:16,968
What's going on, for Christ sake?
What's happening, huh?

839
01:15:17,079 --> 01:15:19,912
This is only for your own safety.

840
01:15:34,162 --> 01:15:37,427
I guess nobody's been in this one
for a couple of years.

841
01:15:37,533 --> 01:15:41,128
You'll be able
to get some rest, yes, sir.

842
01:15:46,441 --> 01:15:49,968
It's a little dusty in here,
but it's clean.

843
01:15:50,078 --> 01:15:52,103
Come on in.

844
01:16:04,760 --> 01:16:07,957
- I hope you don't mind
no sheets and no pillowcases.
- No.

845
01:16:08,063 --> 01:16:09,963
- I'll get you some, though.
- No, please.

846
01:16:10,065 --> 01:16:13,728
Okay, okay, don't worry.
I won't leave this car.

847
01:16:13,835 --> 01:16:16,167
