866
01:21:46,434 --> 01:21:48,698
<i>No.</i>

867
01:21:48,803 --> 01:21:51,567
No. No.

868
01:23:14,422 --> 01:23:16,549
Stop!

869
01:23:56,865 --> 01:23:58,355
Kenny.

870
01:24:02,337 --> 01:24:03,702
