874
01:25:32,227 --> 01:25:34,388
<i>- Clear out!
- Get out of the way, you guys.</i>

875
01:25:34,496 --> 01:25:37,465
<i>- Back up!
- Come on. Back up, damn it.</i>

876
01:25:37,565 --> 01:25:39,931
Get out of the way.
Come on!

877
01:25:40,034 --> 01:25:42,525
Clear the way back there.

878
01:26:19,541 --> 01:26:22,738
