Would you like a cup of coffee?

879
01:26:22,844 --> 01:26:24,812
No, thanks.

880
01:27:53,735 --> 01:27:56,260
Hi. Listen, why don't you
come on back now.

881
01:27:56,371 --> 01:28:00,137
