this place gives me the creeps.

882
01:28:01,342 --> 01:28:03,242
Okay.

883
01:28:42,417 --> 01:28:45,113
Why don't you come back
and join the...

884
01:28:45,219 --> 01:28:47,619
Join us. Come on.

885
01:29:04,906 --> 01:29:06,874
There's the light.

886
01:29:08,109 --> 01:29:11,169
Lord, that's beautiful.

887
01:29:12,847 --> 01:29:16,283
Go back and start the report,
Charlie. I'll bring her on in.

888
01:29:16,384 --> 01:29:18,352
Okay.

889
01:29:21,322 --> 01:29:23,313
- Got it?
- I got her.

890
01:29:23,424 --> 01:29:25,392
Okay.

891
01:31:01,389 --> 01:31:03,414
What the hell?

892
01:31:07,061 --> 01:31:10,622
Hey, Alana.

893
01:31:17,472 --> 01:31:20,066
Carne!

894
01:31:20,174 --> 01:31:23,007
